data.description: Welcome to a truly remarkable home that offers an exceptional blend of space and outdoor amenities on an expansive half-acre lot that is completely fenced in for privacy. This exquisite property presents an unparalleled opportunity to enjoy an enviable Florida lifestyle with all the bells and whistles you desire. Situated on a sprawling plot of land, this home offers the perfect canvas for outdoor enthusiasts and those who appreciate a beautifully landscaped environment. Stepping onto the property, you'll immediately be captivated by the striking outdoor deck that has just been renovated and overlooks a stunning view. This home has just been painted on the outside and offers new solar panels, giving this house excellent efficiency. The 10kw solar panels, new solar water heater, new windows, and an electric car charging station reduce your living cost.   Walking through the home, you will see a fully renovated kitchen with granite countertops, a  backsplash, new cabinets, and stainless steel appliances.  Furthermore, Besides the outdoor amenities, the home offers many features to enhance your comfort and lifestyle. This home also features a mother-in-law suite on the first floor with an office or four bedrooms. You have a large main bedroom and an adjacent laundry room with a sink. Enjoy the completely renovated bathrooms and two large-sized bedrooms for your family. The staircase leading to your upstairs great room and large kitchen is perfect for entertaining. You have a large dining area and eating space in the kitchen. This home has everything a family would want: close to I-4, shopping, schools, lakes, and highways.
